name: Planet Rose Quartz
description: Planet Rose Quartz is the planet of pure love. This planet allows you to find love for oneself and others. It activates the heart chakra and heals it. There is unconditional love and infinite peace on this planet. Here one becomes receptive to beauty of all kinds, and develops the ability to accept parts of yourself in a loving manner. This planet is made with real rose quartz. It glows differently under UV light, regular light, and no light.
